traceRecord.$descriptionTemplate: Log records correspond to server logs

 Log files are automatically compressed.

Only available in development mode !!!
This will write new logs following 'test' configuration and then propagate same writes on every processes handled by the load balancer.

traceRecord.$services.download.$descript: Concatenate every log content in one compressed file.
